snippet.title: Unicorn Overlord — Announcement Trailer | Nintendo Switch, Xbox Series X|S, PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
Liberate your kingdom and reclaim your destiny in Unicorn Overlord! 👑

Traverse the vibrant world of Fevrith and cultivate a grand army with over 60 unique characters in this tactical fantasy RPG.

The adventure begins on March 8, 2024. Wishlist on Nintendo Switch today!

Add Unicorn Overlord to your Nintendo Switch wishlist: https://atlus.link/uonswish
